                  <div>
                    <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">4. EXPECTATIONS FOR ALL PARTICIPANTS</h5>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                      <div>
                        <h6 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-1">4.1 Respect</h6>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-2">All participants are expected to treat others with respect and dignity. This includes, but is not limited to:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 text-sm ml-4 space-y-1">
                          <li><strong>Respect for Individuals:</strong> Treat fellow players, guests, visitors, and staff with courtesy and respect, regardless of physical characteristics, athletic ability, age, ancestry, colour, race, citizenship, ethnic origin, creed, disability, family status, economic or marital status, gender identity or expression, or sexual orientation.</li>
                          <li><strong>Appropriate Attire:</strong> Wear safe and appropriate clothing. Avoid attire with offensive logos, designs, or language.</li>
                          <li><strong>Prohibition of Harassment:</strong> Harassment of any kind‚Äîverbal, physical, or emotional‚Äîis strictly prohibited.</li>
                          <li><strong>Language and Behaviour:</strong> Avoid the use of profanity, inappropriate language, bullying, or intimidation.</li>
                          <li><strong>Sportsmanship:</strong> Demonstrate ethical conduct, sportsmanship, and leadership at all times. Acknowledge great plays and positively promote the sport.</li>
