                          <li><strong>Physical Limits:</strong> Be mindful of your physical condition and avoid over-exertion during play.</li>
                          <li><strong>Court Safety:</strong> If a ball from another court enters your court, immediately stop play by announcing "ball on court." Resume play only after the ball is returned.</li>
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                      
                      <div>
